quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  95,1,Ka Feikha le Olive
  95,2,Le ka Thaba ea Sinai
  95,3,Le ka motse o ts’ireletsong
  95,4,Ruri! Re hlotse motho ka tlholeho e babatsehang
  95,5,Eaba Re mo kokobetsa ka boemo bo tlase-tlase
  95,6,"Ntle le feela ea kholoang a etsa liketso tse lokileng, bao moputso oa bona o ke ke oa sitoa"
  95,7,Ke eng joale se ka o emang pele malebana le kahlolo
  95,8,Na ha se Allah Moahloli Ea Seli